    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TimeSaver.DaySaver, TimeSaver.NightSaver

    public abstract class TimeSaver
extends net.minecraft.block.Block
    When this block exists in the world, the world will remain at the indicated time.
    Extended by TimeSaver.DaySaver and TimeSaver.NightSaver.
    If both of these blocks exist in the world, both blocks have no effect.
